This is gray2snd, a utility that maps grayscale bitmaps into sound
files.

 ==============================================================================

Prerequisites

    * libsndfile-1.0.3 (http://www.zip.com.au/~erikd/libsndfile/).
    * popt-1.6.3 (ftp://ftp.rpm.org/pub/rpm/dist/rpm-4.1.x/).
    * fftw-2.1.3 (http://www.fftw.org/).

    An image manipulation program capable of writing out raw eight-bit
grayscale images will help.  I recommend ImageMagick
(http://www.imagemagick.com/).

 ==============================================================================

Building

    ./configure
    make
    make install

 ==============================================================================

Example Usage

    gray2snd --size=256x256 test.gray test.wav
